        "option_b_result": "CORRECT - If a critical skill gap necessary to overcome unforeseen technical challenges is not addressed, the team will likely be unable to meet the project's technical requirements. This will directly result in reduced quality of deliverables (as problems remain unsolved or poorly implemented) and potentially a reduction in the agreed-upon project scope (as certain features become impossible to deliver). This is a direct consequence of inadequate team capabilities.",
