        "additional_notes": "This question focuses on the consequences of neglecting a critical skill gap within the 'Develop Team' process. When a team lacks the necessary expertise to overcome unforeseen technical challenges, the most direct and probable outcome is that the project will be unable to deliver the planned scope at the required quality. This emphasizes the importance of proactively identifying and addressing skill gaps to maintain project integrity. The incorrect options represent unlikely or indirect consequences; significant skill gaps do not typically lead to improved schedules or motivation, but rather to fundamental performance issues that threaten the project's core deliverables. The scenario highlights a direct cause-and-effect relationship between team capability and project success metrics.",
